snippet.textDisplay:
Not commenting on this song but I didnt really enjoy this season of Coke studio, this season has destroyed the reputation of Coke studio for me.  From lal meri pat to Dama dam mast qalanadar all the songs were below avg. The only above average songs were Ronay na dia and Katay na katay re. 
Please create the music that we can be proud of. Not the bollywoodish commercial songs. I wonder why Rohail Hyatt is still working for Coca Cola as music consultant but not producing coke studio
